成），创造了工业化条件下一步生物合成蛋白质收率最高85%的世界纪录。 该项研究以含一氧化碳、二氧化碳的工业尾气和氨水为主要原料，“无中生有”制造新型饲料蛋白资源乙醇梭菌蛋白，将无机的氮和碳转化为有机的氮和碳，实现了从0 到1的自主创新，具有完全自主知识产权。 以工业化生产1000万吨乙醇梭菌蛋白（蛋白含量83%）计，相当于2800万吨进口大豆（蛋白含量30%）当量，“不与人争粮、不与粮争地”，开辟了一条低成本非传统动植物资源生产优质饲料蛋白质的新途径，可减排二氧化碳2.5亿吨，节省耕地10亿亩（以平均亩产大豆300斤计）。 我国首次实现从一氧化碳到蛋白质的合成并形成万吨级工业产能 继二氧化碳合成淀粉之后，我国首次实现从一氧化碳到蛋白质的合成并形成万吨级工业产能。 我国首次实现从一氧化碳到蛋白质的合成并形成万吨级工业产能 https://feeds-drcn.cloud.huawei.com.cn/landingpage/latest?docid=1051054ucms_8AmUFNJO2dM&to_app=hwbrowser&dy_scenario=today3&tn=d47f5f40067045dbf4af959ee396fba254fd4527e5ac298ce02739f25376b1a9&share_to=link&channel=HW_TRENDING&ctype=news&appid=hwbrowser&cpid=666&r=CN"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlIuZ5dSTlqY0EAMaCDcyNDMwMDUzIOKt+IsGMCs47glAA3IJNDk1NjcxODgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"720 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d8d6df70972672743248f06bfc8f3ee_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1635689231.7004855","card_id":"Q_67870409","target":{"id":67870409,"title":"双十一预售已经付了定金，但不想要了，怎么退款？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/67870409","type":"question","created":1510206031,"answer_count":205,"follower_count":574,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[843,2016,2511,77539,780107],"comment_count":10,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"11 月 1 日就要支付双十一预售的尾款了，但是我不想要了怎么办？https://news.dayoo.com/finance/202110/31/139999_54099415.htm"},"attached_info":"Cj4IlIuZ5dSTlqY0EAMaCDE5Mzc2Nzg4IM/Uj9AFMAo4vgRABHIINjc4NzA0MDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"411 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5d1a2243976988eccf7ac461481c0315_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1635689231.7011936","card_id":"Q_493975306","target":{"id":493975306,"title":"到底应该如何培养一个优秀的小孩？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4939753